vote.title: An ordinance amending Ordinance No. 31330, previously approved on September 18, 2019, authorizing certain transfers and appropriation adjustments for FY 2019-20 for the maintenance and operation of various departments, amending the grants/trusts budgets, and amending the capital budget; and authorize the City Manager to implement those adjustments - Financing:  No cost consideration to the City
